title: Kings Of Rock'n Roll
description:
The Kings of Rock and Roll

Chuck Berry, Jerry Lee Lewis, Bill Haley and Little Richard, 
give high-energy performances in highlights from The London Rock and Roll 
Show at Wembley Stadium in 1972.
